:Register Vehicle;
note right
User opens the vehicle registration form.
end note

:Enter Vehicle Details;
note right
User enters license plate number,
vehicle type, and required details.
end note

:Submit Registration;
note right
User submits the completed
vehicle registration form.
end note

:Validate Vehicle Data;
note right
System verifies that all required
vehicle details are valid.
end note

if (Data Valid?) then (Yes)

  :Save Vehicle Information;
  note right
  System stores the vehicle
  information in the database.
  end note

  :Show Success Confirmation;
  note right
  System displays registration
  success message to the user.
  end note

else (No)

  :Display Error Message;
  note right
  System shows validation errors
  and requests correction.
  end note

endif

stop
